<div class="model fade" id="see-the-need" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <button type="button" class="close glyphicon glyphicon-remove" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
          <a href="https://nepal-relief.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank"><h3 style="color:black;">See the Need</h3> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open"></span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p>This app aims to create transparency between donors and relief centers in disaster areas and optimize logistics for resources needed after the earthquake that hit Nepal on April 25, 2015. The goal is to allow relief centers list their needs - along with the urgency of those needs - and have donors claim those needs and find relief centers to donate to and discover what items are most needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <h4>Tech</h4>
          <div class="tech-container">
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/rails-logo.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/HTML5-Logo.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/CSS3.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/postgresql_logo.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/logo-jquery.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/js.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/handlebars-logo.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
            <%= image_tag('tech-icons/bootstrap-logo.png', class: "tech-pic") %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

